videos.description: No. 18 Missouri's Dru Smith credits handing No. 10 Alabama its first SEC loss to the Tigers "being locked in" for the 68-65 upset.
videos.headline: Smith says Missouri 'one of the best' when focused

videos.description: The No. 18 Tigers build a huge lead and then withstand a furious comeback by No. 10 Alabama to hold on for a 68-65 victory.
videos.headline: Missouri holds off Alabama to give Tide first SEC loss
